Package com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVBasedURLActionDataListBuilder
    Implementation of the URLActionDataListBuilder for files of type 'CSV'.
    URLActionData
    Data Container which holds all necessary information to create and validate a single http request.
    URLActionDataBuilder
    Helper class to build an URLActionData.
    URLActionDataListBuilder
    Abstract class that offers an interface for the implementation of various file type specific List<#URLActionData> Builders.
    URLActionDataListFacade
    Give this class a file path and it tries to construct a List<#URLActionData> from the data in the file via URLActionDataListFacade.buildUrlActions().
    URLActionDataStore
    Data container which holds all the necessary information to grab and store information out of a Http response in order to provide access to them via the URLActionDataStore.interpreter.
    URLActionDataStoreBuilder
    Helper class to build an URLActionDataStore.
    URLActionDataValidation
    Data container which holds all the necessary information to grab and validate information out of a http request.
    URLActionDataValidationBuilder
    Helper class to build an URLActionDataValidation.
    YAMLBasedURLActionDataListBuilder
    Implementation of the URLActionDataListBuilder for files of type 'YAML'.
